cosφ-P/Pn exit
voltage
Specifies the voltage threshold for
exiting reactive power compensation
based on the cosφ-P curve.
-
Reactive power
adjustment time
Specifies the adjustment time for the
reactive power to reach the target
value during reactive power
adjustment.
-
