Reference Power Parameters
Parameter Setting Description
Apparent power
baseline
Set the apparent power baseline for power scheduling. The value
cannot be greater than the maximum apparent power.
Active power baseline Set the active power baseline for power scheduling. The value cannot
be greater than the maximum active power.
Calibrating the Energy Yield
Parameter Setting Description
Total energy yield
adjustment
A calibrating coefficient for the total energy yield to ensure that the
reported energy yield is consistent with the actual energy yield at the
grid connection point
Adjustment of total
power supply from grid
A calibrating coefficient for the total power supply from the grid to
ensure that the reported energy yield is consistent with the actual
power supply from grid
