Periodic PID
runtime
Specifies the running duration of the PID module when the
PID module and IMD operate in cycle mode. The value of
this parameter ranges from 60 min to 480 min. The IMD is
shut down when the PID module is running.
Periodic IMD
runtime
Specifies the running duration of the IMD when the PID
module and IMD operate in cycle mode. The value of this
parameter ranges from 15 min to 480 min. The PID module
is standby when the IMD is running.
