Power lowering
adjustment period
Specifies the period for lowering the device output
power.
Maximum protection
time
Specifies the maximum duration from the time when
the SmartLogger detects feed-in to the time when the
device output power reaches 0.
Suggestion: Set this parameter based on the
maximum feed-in duration allowed by the power grid
company.
Power raising threshold When the power supply from the grid reaches this
