down for protection when the grid-connection
point power exceeds the threshold and remains in
this condition for the specified time threshold.
SmartLogger3000
User Manual 6 WebUI Operations
Issue 20 (2024-04-15) Copyright © Huawei Technologies Co., Ltd. 298

Parameter Description
Upper feed-in power
threshold for inverter
shutdown
The default value is 0. This parameter specifies the
