Mode SmartLogger
Port
Requirement Remarks
DRM0 AI2–AI4 ● When S0 is turned on, the
inverters shut down.
● When S0 is turned off, the
inverters are connected to the
power grid.
-
DRM5 DI1 When S5 is turned on, the
